    "name": "MailPop",
    "steam_appid": 2389250,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389250/extras/c69904a6a60335ff49c6fc70909fa788.avif?t=1759753026\" width=800 height=504 /></span>Mail Pop is a game where you’ll have to smash your keyboard to write an email while hilarious and chaotic pop-ups try to drive you insane. Destroy those ads with a furious click, type as fast as you can, and reach ultimate enlightenment and relaxation in Mail Pop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you attack with the keyboard or defend with the mouse? Decide which strategy works best in each of the 4 brand-new levels of Mail Pop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover new types of pop-ups... and DESTROY THEM.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389250/extras/7c135ce80d1f284a29d46c423569e9f0.avif?t=1759753026\" width=798 height=466 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get the highest multiplier in the whole office.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mash out your emails and send them before time runs out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389250/extras/dd0054b8c0f125730bcb5eb1d97d3696.avif?t=1759753026\" width=754 height=495 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock all achievements before carpal tunnel claims another victim and your coworkers start envying you at the coffee machine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can now enjoy the incredibly relaxing Mail Pop experience in English! Type those emails in multiple languages! (Well… two, to be exact.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389250/extras/3b429a8635fea917d0735e50e0972a35.avif?t=1759753026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389250/extras_big/3b429a8635fea917d0735e50e0972a35.avif?t=1759753026 width=800 height=314 /></span></p>",
